               <text>ANDY OXY CO. ASHEVILLE, NC (828) 258-0271 AIR, COMPRESSED U.S.P. UN1002 DO NOT REMOVE THIS PRODUCT LABEL. NON-FLAMMABLE GAS 2 CONTENTS PRESSURE MEDICAL AIR, U.S.P. CAUTION: HIGH PRESSURE GAS. MAY ACCELERATE COMBUSTION. Keep oil and grease away. Use only with equipment designated for compressed air service and rated for cylinder pressure. User shall secure cylinder in use and storage. Use in upright position. Close valve after each use, and when empty. Keep valve protection cap in place when not in use, if so equipped. Use in accordance with MSDS. CAUTION: Rx ONLY. WARNING: Administration of medical air to humans for breathing maintenance should be by adequately trained personnel experienced in the use and administration of medical air. CAS 25635-88-5 RETURN WITH 25 PSIG.<renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
